// Stopband ≥ 120 dB for all stages (Stage 1: -125.8 dB measured).
// Audio passband 0–20 kHz, images rejected ≥ 120 dB.
//
// Coefficients generated by gen_halfband_coeffs.py (Kaiser window, β=12.27).
// ============================================================

